00059     int nx = 5000;
00060         CHPMultiDataData data(TEST_FILE1);
00061         data.SetEntryCount(GenotypeMultiDataType, ng, 10);
00062         data.SetEntryCount(ExpressionMultiDataType, nx, 10);

00066

00068     gn.call = 0;

00072         gn.name = IntToString(i);
00073             writer->WriteEntry(gn);

00075         writer->SeekToDataSet(ExpressionMultiDataType);
00076     ex.quantification = 0;
00077     for (int i=0; i<nx; i++)
